      <title>澳大利亚监管机构与银行合作监督人工智能的采用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/australian-regulators-working-with-banks-to-monitor-ai-adoption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚储备银行周四表示，澳大利亚金融监管机构正在与业界合作，以了解和监控人工智能的采用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/australian-regulators-working-with-banks-to-monitor-ai-adoption</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
