      <title>新世界集团因首席执行官郑志刚辞职而暂停交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/new-world-development-halts-trading-amid-ceo-departure-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，新世界发展有限公司首席执行官郑志刚即将卸任，该公司股票于周四上午暂停在香港的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/new-world-development-halts-trading-amid-ceo-departure-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 00:53:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收购公司提高韩国锌业的收购报价，将公司估值提高至 116 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/mbk-raises-korea-zinc-offer-price-to-attract-more-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MBK Partners 将其对韩国锌业公司控制权的主动出价提高了约 14%，推动该股创下历史新高，对这家全球最大锌冶炼厂的估值达到 15.5 万亿韩元（116 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/mbk-raises-korea-zinc-offer-price-to-attract-more-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:59:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
